<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause author="Brandon Kiem" dateTime="2021-03-12T08:28:23" id="_c6c01603-e978-4c6f-95b0-5d1710b3e8c6" outputclass="ncc-clause" type="insert"><meta><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 7a"/><facet building="Class 7b"/><facet building="Class 8"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet climate="Climate zone 8"/></meta><sptc>4.2.9</sptc><title id="_30ea7e15-465c-456f-98ef-5228ee825b18">Edge rebates</title><archive-num>2019: 3.2.2.7</archive-num><subclause id="_c060896b-73cb-4c41-87eb-b96ce3b5b082" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_504b6ac3-98a8-4318-843f-6493dd944561">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Edge rebates for slab-on-ground and stiffened raft with masonry <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1214_0.9.0.xml#_d9f8479e-3794-41cf-ab60-e1588241810e" id="_e0d42e9a-ad51-42b8-b358-4b7f1ca37abe" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">cavity</xref> or veneer construction must comply with the following:</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_1c54d755-0ace-4c65-b1bf-8f3a3b7f1f6b">The rebate must not be less than 20 mm.</li><li id="_11907f4d-cac3-49f8-a5b8-e0461578b3a1">The edge rebate must be flashed and drained in accordance with <xref format="dita" href="qpp://assets/1860#_9dad7301-0c09-495c-8e8e-94653b60c8fb" id="_44f3b4e7-ba43-44c1-a07a-dfd4f0a1e112" publishing-id="vol2" referencetype="Text" scope="external" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">H2D4</xref> and where it cannot be flashed, it must be filled with mortar.</li></ol></subclause><callout id="_752248ff-89c5-404e-877c-f0962feaef0a"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><p>See <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1051_1.7.0.xml#_018141a1-fe7c-4ed4-88a4-72ad7e3a4d87" id="_ef38300c-6815-4495-a84c-989c8d3348f5" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">4.2.21</xref> for minimum edge beam details. For single skin or framed walls with external cladding, rebates are not required.</p></callout></clause>